{
  "stem": "964.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Until the water came in into-- into Krzemieniec, we had-- hundreds of bottles were busted, falling apart, because [NON-ENGLISH] when-- water, when freezes, expands.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So all of us were processed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was one case.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Another case, sugar, you can keep it in no matter what degree.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It won't disintegrate or melt away except if you put it between water.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So sugar, they sent by airplane from Kiev to-- to-- to Krzemieniec by airplane.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then it was a typhus epidemic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So the-- the-- the-- the-- the-- to fight the typhus, the-- the anti bacteria medicine, they send it by train.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Till they came, all was gone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is the sabotage, you know, the [NON-ENGLISH] sabotage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyway, so we-- we were there, I working at the pharmaceutical company, my uncle who worked in the bakery.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the-- the war started in 1941, the Russian German war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I was greeting the Germans again, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The second time, they were liberating me, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knew what's all about.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I told to my uncle, the younger-- he has a brother that said, let's go over the border into Russian, the old border.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had passports, everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we shouldn't have any problems.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "While we were going, we found out that all of these people that-- that don't have passports issued in Russia, they won't let them take-- they won't let-- they don't let them through the border.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the people that, like us, that took away the passports, you're-- you're nobody.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had to go back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Had to wait, had no choice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Krzemieniec.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we started-- we started out to go back into-- deep into Russia to escape the Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I knew already who they are, what to expect from them.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
